itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",2 weeks ago,"President Biden has spent almost a week in office. How was it? Pretty good. Not exceptional, but not bad. Normal. GZERO Media  |  #QuickTake : #Biden   #uspolitics   #gzero   #geopolitics https://lnkd.in/eBpWS5R 
 
 
