 the job so the tendency is to just agree and get to work. I get it. But nobody is offended by a good negotiation. If a company is motivated to hire you and you are motivated to work at a company, then a good discussion about the job makes everyone happier. VERY IMPORTANT: A good salary negotiation is win-win. Both sides get more motivated. The pie gets larger... 
 
 
