ie Endowment, and the IMF's Committee of Eminent Persons. He is currently a board member of the NBER, Barclays and Under Armour, and co-chairs the capital campaign for Cambridge. He has been chair of the Microsoft Investment Advisory Board since 2007He holds a master's degree and doctorate (economics) from Oxford and received his bachelor and master degrees from Cambridge",7 months ago,"FYI, my thoughts on the implications of today's economic data. https://lnkd.in/gUbV8Yu #economy   #jobs   #employment   #unemployment   #markets   #economics   #bopinion   #growth   #gdp   #bloomberg 
 
 
