itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",1 month ago,"Signal writer Carlos Santamaria's  #TopStories2020  pick Abiy Ahmed Ali won the Nobel Peace Prize for making peace with Eritrea. Now he's at war with a region of his own country... with Eritrean support. Sign up for  GZERO Media 's Signal newsletter👇 https://bit.ly/2VTN1nT https://lnkd.in/dDVHxCv 
 
 
