itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",3 weeks ago,Sage advice,[],image,['https://media-exp1.licdn.com/dms/image/C4D22AQHJM5s6Z2LHqg/feedshare-shrink_800/0/1611093165003?e=1616025600&v=beta&t=H7gMimZsJpzKWyKTCCCiCftCbFrTs6Fu5QzgFIwq9EY'],0,0,[],429,13,,,,,
