itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",1 week ago,"‪Most important (heck, almost miraculous) vaccine takeaway: 100% effectiveness at preventing serious illness or death.‬",[],image,['https://media-exp1.licdn.com/dms/image/C4E22AQGfAVax5hMLew/feedshare-shrink_800/0/1612294742509?e=1616025600&v=beta&t=5NnTXz8hWhK3XfeCkITZl5OI3KP4accD8Y_GpdEBwv4'],0,0,[],1376,127,,,,,
