itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",2 weeks ago,The Creation of Bernie,[],image,['https://media-exp1.licdn.com/dms/image/C4D22AQF6_vIrTo3eQg/feedshare-shrink_800/0/1611520340011?e=1616025600&v=beta&t=f_jaSDzc2p8qdV26yh10R_kX3nRWiyZSOY44xWs9vfo'],0,0,[],3612,114,,,,,
