itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",1 month ago,"As more people get vaccinated, mortality rates are going to go down significantly. As it does, there needs to be more focus on the economic side of the equation. World  #In60Seconds   #gzero   #world   #globalpolitics   #navalny   #russia   #usa   #britain   #covid19   https://lnkd.in/eAFnRGK 
 
 
