itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",3 months ago,"When Biden takes over, he won't mind having fewer US troops on the ground in Afghanistan: World  #In60Seconds   GZERO Media https://lnkd.in/eAFnRGK 
 
 
