itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",2 months ago,Snow days are awesome. Jefferson County gets it.,[],image,['https://media-exp1.licdn.com/dms/image/C4E22AQF1yPuWUXM62Q/feedshare-shrink_800/0/1608236527325?e=1616025600&v=beta&t=QvK1kfBmXo8f9w0-dYu4ecppGkd7jKOUzGTGmaFY29c'],0,0,[],765,23,,,,,
