itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",1 month ago,"Countries like Israel and the UK have been praised for their COVID-19 vaccination drives. Here's a look at the countries that have vaccinated the largest percentages of their populations so far. #GraphicTruth   GZERO Media 
 
 
