itution. He received his bachelor's degree in international relations from Tulane University.Ian established Eurasia Group with just $25,000 in 1998. Today, the company has offices in New York, Washington, San Francisco, London, Brasilia, Sao Paulo, Singapore, and Tokyo, as well as a network of experts and resources in 90 countries.",1 month ago,"Brexit breakup is finally here. With what the UK has done to limit its connections with the EU, sadly, London won't be the global city it used to be.  #Brexit   #US   #UK   #EU   #London   #globalcities   #Brexitdeal   GZERO Media  | World  #In60Seconds   https://lnkd.in/eAFnRGK 
 
 
